South Korea’s Financial Regulator Has No Plan for Second Exchange Operator

-- B y   S o o k y u n g   S e o
-- 
2011-03-20T22:26:33Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-20/south-korea-s-financial-regulator-has-no-plan-for-second-exchange-operator.html
  South Korea ’s financial regulator
says it is not considering setting up a second exchange
operator, denying the Maeil Business Newspaper report that it is
seeking to set up a second bourse operator to increase
competition. The Financial Service Commission commented on a
second exchange in an e-mailed statement.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
